<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to {{ user.companyName }}</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Welcome, {{ user.adminFirstName }}!</h1>
    <p>
        Thank you for registering <strong>{{ user.companyName }}</strong> with our HRMS platform.
    </p>

    <p>
        Please verify your email address to complete the setup process:
    </p>

    <p>
        <a href="{{ url }}">Click here to verify your email</a>
    </p>

    <p>
        If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
        {{ url }}
    </p>

    <p>
        Best regards,<br>
        The HRMS Team
    </p>
</body>
</html>
